<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>填写基本信息</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
    <META HTTP-EQUIV="Pragma" CONTENT="no-cache">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <script>
        var ROOT = "__ROOT__";//网站根目录地址,例:/根目录
        var APP = "__APP__";//当前应用（入口文件）地址,例:/根目录/index.php
        var APP_NAME = "__APP_NAME__";//网站应用根目录,例:/根目录/应用目录
        var IMG = "__IMG__";
        var STATIC = "__PUBLIC__/static";
        var UPFILE = "__UPFILE__";
        var THEME = "__THEME__";
    </script>
    <!--标准mui.css-->
    <css href="__CSS__/mui.min.css" />
    <style>
        .mui-content-padded{
            padding-top:20px;
        }
        .mui-btn-primary{
            background-color:#fe6700;
            border:1px solid #fe6700;

        }
        .mui-content .mui-title1{
            margin-top:45px;
            color: #000000;
            text-align:center;
        }
    </style>

<body>
<div class="mui-content">
    <p class="mui-title1">填写基本信息</p>
    <div  class="mui-card">
        <form class="mui-input-group">
            <div class="mui-input-row">
                <label>手机号</label>
                <input id='account' type="text" class="mui-input-clear mui-input" placeholder="请输入手机号">
            </div>
            <div class="mui-input-row">
                <label>密码</label>
                <input id='password' type="password" class="mui-input-clear mui-input" placeholder="请输入密码">
            </div>
            <div class="mui-input-row">
                <label>验证码</label>
                <input id='vercode' type="text" class="mui-input-clear mui-input" placeholder="">
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="mui-content-padded"  style="margin-top:-10px;">
        <button  id="getcode" style="width:50%;margin-left:140px;height:40px;padding-top:5px;" class="mui-btn mui-btn-block mui-btn-primary">获取验证码</button>
    </div>
    <div class="mui-content-padded">
     <button  id="submit" style="width:78%;margin:auto;height:45px;padding-top:10px;" class="mui-btn mui-btn-block mui-btn-primary">确定</button>
    </div>
    <div class="mui-content-padded">
    <p>填写手机号是为了保证与我们的小宝账号进行绑定,绑定后方可查看做任务</p>
    </div>
</div>


<js href="__JS__/mui.min.js" />
<js href="__STATIC__/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"/>
</body>
</html>